snippet.title: Funkin' at Freddy's v1: Afton Full week | Song 1 "Celebrate" Gameplay (Old)
snippet.description:
Here's a gameplay showcase for song 1 of the Funkin' at Freddy's Afton week! 

You can find the page for Funkin' at Freddy's on Gamebanana and Gamejolt!
Gamebanana - https://gamebanana.com/mods/360682
Gamejolt - https://gamejolt.com/games/FunkinAtFreddysMod/823267
Listen to the song on its own here - https://youtu.be/qH80X2qBBdo
